In order for the speaker NPM package to build on Intel Edison yocto, add the ALSA source code.

Get the ALSA source
ftp://ftp.alsa-project.org/pub/lib/
Create the /usr/include/alsa directory if needed
Copy all .h files from the source /include folder to local /usr/include/alsa

It is also necessary to create a link to the latest libasound libarary for backward compatibility

ln -s /usr/lib/libasound.so.2.2.0 /usr/lib/libasound.so
